{"tid":1163040,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同男朋友同年/ 細過自己係咪唔會有好結果？","createTime":"2019-05-20T08:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T14:32:41.000Z","uid":67334,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f9eea652c4a2e2689857872abb0f096eb7f37696","tid":1163040,"uid":67334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:18:02.000Z","msg":"同男友同年<br />\n通常男人都係30歲後先會結婚<br />\n加上大家嘅家境都唔算係好好<br />\n唔知要儲錢儲到幾時<br />\n今年21讀埋書下年就岀嚟做野<br />\n佢仲好似想讀埋個master先<br />\n等到30唔緊要<br />\n但會怕佢到時嫌棄自己<br />\n到時人老珠黃乜都冇<br />\n<br />\n搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceac5dfdd73bd795de5101378eb22e997e4a4fef","tid":1163040,"uid":174285,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:20:04.000Z","msg":"關年齡咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe29f2c37cdb877d4857fd525cccc4fdf8afcf9","tid":1163040,"uid":251746,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:22:55.000Z","msg":"咁你搵個五十歲，有車有樓咪得囉，唔使儲錢啦。<br />\n你地仲後生，係要捱下儲下錢㗎啦，面對現實啦，擔心咁多做咩丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03a0a2c46e0bf30281514025adb2b29bab21894","tid":1163040,"uid":228793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:24:53.000Z","msg":"我都唔知 女友大我兩年4個月 我24 佢已經27去梗28<br />\n<br />\n但我事業仲係發展階段 大約20k 公屋仔 儲蓄唔夠10皮 唔知點結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過多三年佢已經30 我先27，28 好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08029597f77e2850aebe833a03404137702c2d9e","tid":1163040,"uid":100766,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:31:40.000Z","msg":"唔關年齡事<br />\n但佢仲想讀master<br />\n注定你出黎做野份糧就用黎補貼佢學費生活費<br />\n直至佢考到master搵到份高薪厚職<br />\n仲要搏佢到時唔會飛起你<br />\n<br />\n咁先係最大問題"},{"pid":"c2c0eb284b7e7345f4ca8338e98b880265917a71","tid":1163040,"uid":12909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc